<p><span class=jammenu><a href="#setup">Setup</a></span>--data acquisition or offline sorting</p>
<p><span class=jammenu><a href="#control">Control</a></span>--data acquisition or offline sorting</p>
<p><span class=jammenu><a href="#histogram">Histogram</a></span>--create, calibrate and zero histograms</p>
<p><span class=jammenu><a href="#gate">Gate</a></span>--create, set, display gates</p>
<p><span class=jammenu><a href="#scalers">Scalers</a></span>--configure, display,zero scalers and monitors</p>
<p><span class=jammenu><a href="#preferences">Preferences</a></span>--display options</p>
